<item>
            <title>[SOLR-15368] Bad favicon logo - contains white background</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15368</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On any modern webpage, the favicon has a transparent background.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example - look at Github&apos;s logo as opposed to Solr&apos;s logo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13024530/13024530_image-2021-04-23-19-15-18-355.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In fact, there is actually a good logo on Solr&apos;s Jira site (uploaded on this very issue):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13024528/13024528_image-2021-04-23-19-18-55-304.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suggest fixing the favicon and replace the background.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
